<refsect2>
<title><anchor id="gok-settingsdialog-refresh"/>gok_settingsdialog_refresh ()</title>
<indexterm><primary>gok_settingsdialog_refresh</primary></indexterm><programlisting><link linkend="void">void</link>        gok_settingsdialog_refresh      (void);</programlisting>
<para>
Refreshes the dialog controls. This should be called after the user has resized the keyboard
(which causes the key size to change) or if the gok data has changed.</para>
<para>

</para></refsect2>
